name: Any Inu
description: Any Inu: The First Omnichain Dogcoin Powered by Axelar's ITS (Interchain Token Service) $AI is a revolutionary memecoin like no other currently operating on 20 blockchains, making it the most widely distributed memecoin ever! With a total max supply of 420,690,000,000 coins, it is strategically allocated across these networks. By leveraging Axelar's bridge, $AI enables seamless transfers across EVM-compatible chains, including Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, Avalanche, Base, Fantom, Polygon, and many more. Additionally, Wormhole's bridge ensures effortless transactions between Ethereum and Solana. This multi-chain integration significantly enhances $AI's utility and accessibility, empowering the community to unite and thrive within a truly decentralized ecosystem. Multichain is the future!
